title: 4  Data Dictionary

This document contains a data dictionary for the patient data collected in the study. Each variable is defined below:







Variable Name
Description




record_id
The number assigned to each individual patient (starting at 1)


redcap_event_name
Describes the visit when the data was recorded


sex_dashboard
Sex of patient (Male, Female, Not Reported)


graft_dashboard2
Patient graft type


visit_sex
Sex of patient (Male, Female, Not Reported)


visit_graft
Patient graft type


age
Age of patient at time of visit (in years)


height_m
Patient height (in meters)


mass_kg
Patient weight (in kilograms)


bmi
Body Mass Index (BMI) of patient


tss
Time Since Surgery (in months)


tss_dashboard
String of the time since surgery range (in months)


ikdc
International Knee Documentation Committee score


koos_pain
Knee Injury and Osteoarthritis Outcome Score pain score


acl_rsi
ACL Return to Sport Index score (mental readiness post-surgery)


acl_sh
Single Hop Score for ACLR side


con_sh
Single Hop Score for contralateral side


sh_lsi
Single Hop LSI (limb symmetry index), % injured vs. uninjured limb


acl_th
Triple Hop Score for ACLR side


con_th
Triple Hop Score for contralateral side


th_lsi
Triple Hop LSI (limb symmetry index), % injured vs. uninjured limb
